                <h1>How to Change Background Color in Canva: A Step-by-Step Guide</h1>
                <p>To change the background color in Canva, open your design and click on the background area. A color palette will appear on the toolbar. Choose from the available colors or enter a hex code for a specific shade. You can also use the "Background" tab on the left sidebar for more options. Click on the desired color to apply it instantly!</p>
